### 1 Create Tenant

POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "legalName": "Professor Company",
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "fullName": "Admin",
  "baseCurrency": "USD"
}

